Files:
- plugins/carta/src/index.ts (fix isReady() method, line 62)

Context:
Current isReady() (lines 61-63):
  async isReady(): Promise<boolean> {
    return isAuthenticated();
  }

waitForAuth is exported from carta-api.ts. Other plugins use:
  async isReady(): Promise<boolean> {
    return waitForAuth();
  }

Fix — simply change to:
  async isReady(): Promise<boolean> {
    return waitForAuth();
  }

Make sure waitForAuth is imported from './carta-api.js' — it likely is already since isAuthenticated is imported.

Constraints:
- Do NOT change carta-api.ts
- Do NOT change the waitForAuth() implementation
- The import at the top of index.ts should already include both isAuthenticated and waitForAuth
